spec registry_demo
"""
Registry-style references demo.

Uses canonical @... spec and type references. Resolution only
calls the Registry for @... identifiers that are not already in the
loaded spec set. The specs @org/example/helper and @lemma/std/finance
are defined below in this same file, so they are loaded with the
workspace and the Registry is never called. If they were not present
locally, the engine would call the Registry (e.g. LemmaBase); a
missing spec would then produce a Registry error.
"""

type money from @lemma/std/finance

fact unit_price : 5 eur

rule line_total:
  unit_price * 2 in eur
